injuries.comment: Parsons is questionable to play in Game Two of the Western Conference Quarterfinals.
Harris is questionable to play in Game Two of the Western Conference Quarterfinals.
Beverley has opted for season-ending surgery on the torn ligaments in his wrist.
Papanikolaou is likely to play on Friday (4/10).
McDaniel's has been diagnosed with a non-displaced right elbow fracture, and he is doubtful to return during the postseason.
Motiejunas underwent back surgery on Thursday (4/9) and will miss the rest of the season.
